    <section name="UploadValve">
      <subsection name="Description">
        <p>The Upload component is the implementation of the pipeline processing valve,
        that is run at very early stage of the pipeline processing. When it discovers the
        "multipart/form-data" it starts to process the request storing the uploaded items into 
        the context.
         </p>
      </subsection>
      
